== output_bit_on_immediate (light ring ON) ==

Target: turn on the light ring.
Word to set: 0x0201 = lamp_enable (0x0200) | cam_light_pair (0x0001).

host → ctrl  (8 bytes)
14 00 00 00  01 02 00 00
^^                                       opcode = 0x14 output_bit_on_immediate
   ^^                                    sequence
      ^^                                 aux
         ^^                              pad
            ^^^^^^^^^^^                  bit_mask = 0x00000201

ctrl → host  (echo)
14 00 ...

To turn it back off:

host → ctrl  (8 bytes)
15 00 00 00  01 02 00 00
^^                                       opcode = 0x15 output_bit_off_immediate
            ^^^^^^^^^^^                  bit_mask = 0x00000201

CAMERA SWITCH (single atomic write):

host → ctrl  (8 bytes)  switch to UP camera with light
04 00 00 00  00 82 00 00
^^                                       opcode = 0x04 set_outputs_immediate
            ^^^^^^^^^^^                  full output word = 0x00008200
                                         = cam_mux | lamp_enable
